comment.author: 26881258@N07
comment._content: Another view of the Friedrichshafen FF 33j Marinenummer '3033'. This is the official front view of the machine. The official sideview picture was here www.flickr.com/photos/49487266@N07/7585286210/in/photolis... Very fine documentary official picture. Probably at the back of the original picture are stamps that will verify that. Mostly it also carries at the back the frightening text 'NUR FÜR DEN DIENSTGEBRAUCH' [For service use only].
